Hartfield & Co (Pritchard & Bail) Tue thru Fri 8am -6pm; Sat 10am - 6pm; Prichard and Bail; Thu thru Sat 5 - 11pm; A unique experience in cocktail culture founded on pre-prohibition style techniques and fundamentals; all built right inside Hartfield & Co.; Prichard and Bail is a new and curated experience drawing on the ideas and beliefs that cocktails are best made fresh and with quality ingredients; beer is best served from a local source and wine can be a ride along the terrain and vine all contained in a bottle.
